            <bug_when>2012-01-09 10:39:10 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>When building using our continuous integration system the log fills with a lot of |/-\|/-\|/-\|/- characters.

It would be nice to have an option for the generator script that still outputs progress such as &#39;Scanning libraries&#39;, &#39;Collecting classes&#39; but without the progress spinner.

The current quiet option disables the spinner, but it also disables the other messages as well.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
